title: User Stories
---
body:

A set of user stories to inform development of the Frictionless Data ecosystem.

## Personas

- Researcher: A person conducting data-intensive research.
- Publisher: A person or organization looking to publish datasets.
- Developer: A person working on developing software that creates or consumes Data Packages.

## User Stories

User stories are managed on a Trello board which you can view below.  Click through to leave a comment or subscribe to user stories you're interested in. To add a new user story, [open a new issue in our issue tracker](https://github.com/frictionlessdata/specs/issues/new) and we will discuss it with you and add it to the Trello board below.

